      "cooked": "<p>edhe dreads edhe rasta terma te huazuara jane gjithsesi <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/smiley.png?v=5\" title=\":smiley:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":smiley:\"></p>",
