      "created_at": "2016-10-23T00:36:38.074Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Once u go Rasta u can’t go back unless u cut ur hair very very short. Lol Mendohu mire moj. Btw se pelqej fare rasten, si dirty person do na dukesh <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/see_no_evil.png?v=5\" title=\":see_no_evil:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":see_no_evil:\"> Qe nuk la floket lol</p>",
